org.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13)) AND (identifier = 'ecookbook subproject 1' OR LOWER(name) = 'ecookbook subproject 1') ORDER BY projects.id ASC LIMIT "$1"

rewrites.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13) LIMIT 1) AND (identifier = 'ecookbook subproject 1' OR LOWER(name) = 'ecookbook subproject 1') ORDER BY projects.id ASC LIMIT "$1"
